      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Supra Turbo is a masterclass in Japanese performance engineering, featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six equipped with sequential twin-turbochargers. Power is delivered via the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. This specimen retains its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and four-piston ventilated disc brakes, showing no signs of thermal stress or bushing fatigue. The chassis integrity is absolute, with all original VIN tags intact and a pristine undercarriage. Inside, the cockpit is free of UV damage or bolster wear, maintaining the tactile precision of its original ergonomic design. A true collector-grade example of a golden-era grand tourer.",
